OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776780668
OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys appeared in court on
OL,7,FTuesday charged with offences arising
OL,8,Ffrom an assault of a search and rescue
OL,9,Fvolunteer and his dog.
OL,11,FWhile the 13 and 15-year-old boys
OL,12,Fappeared at the Youth Court in
OL,13,FNewtownards, two other defendants,
OL,14,Fanother 15-year-old boy and a 16-year-
OL,15,Fold girl, did not appear.
OL,17,FA defence solicitor for the boy who
OL,18,Fdid not appear, revealed the teenager
OL,19,Fhas received multiple death threats
OL,20,Fand had moved house as a result.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
