CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776780668
OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FIn relation to the girl however, a
OL,7,Fpolice officer told District Judge
OL,8,FAmanda Brady the 16-year-old "is no
OL,9,Fstranger to the court."
OL,11,F"She would have known she had to be
OL,12,Fhere," said the officer.
OL,14,FAs there was no excuse or
OL,15,Fjustification put forward for her
OL,16,Fabsence, Judge Brady said the PPS
OL,17,Fapplication for a warrant "is
OL,18,Fdifficult to resist" so she issued a
OL,19,Fwarrant for her arrest.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@WO]sD@AOUtD@FO]yD@[OUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
