OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776780668
OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FAll four defendants, who cannot be
OL,7,Fnamed because of their ages, are
OL,8,Fjointly charged with affray on High
OL,9,FStreet in Bangor on 27 March this year.
OL,11,FThe boys are also all charged with
OL,12,Fcausing actual bodily harm to Ryan
OL,13,FGray while the 16-year-old girl is
OL,14,Fcharged with common assault of the K9
OL,15,Fsearch and rescue volunteer.
OL,17,FThe 13-year-old and one of the 15-year-
OL,18,Folds are further charged with causing
OL,19,Funnecessary suffering to a dog on the
OL,20,Fsame date.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
