PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776780668
OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FGiving evidence to the court, a
OL,7,Fconstable said she believed she could
OL,8,Fconnect the teenagers to their
OL,9,Frespective offences.
OL,11,FThe two boys who did appear, confirmed
OL,12,Fthey understood the charges against
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,FA prosecuting lawyer told Judge Brady
OL,16,F"the full file will be approximately
OL,17,Ffour weeks" so she was applying for
OL,18,Fthe case to be adjourned.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
