PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776780668
OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FConverting the teenagers' police bail
OL,7,Fto court bail and adjourning the case
OL,8,Fto mid-May, the judge added conditions
OL,9,Fbarring the defendants from contacting
OL,10,Feach other.
OL,12,FIt is understood that Mr Gray, a
OL,13,Ffounder and a volunteer at K9 Search
OL,14,Fand Rescue, was walking with his dog
OL,15,FMax along the High Street in Bangor
OL,16,Fwhen they were attacked by a crowd of
OL,17,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
