OL,3,CTwo teenagers appear in court charged
OL,4,Cwith assault of search volunteer
OL,6,FThe war veteran told local media that
OL,7,Fhe sustained injuries including a
OL,8,Fbroken tooth, broken nose, bruised
OL,9,Feyes and whiplash-type injuries, and
OL,10,Fthat Max had to be taken to the vet to
OL,11,Fbe checked over after he was kicked
OL,12,Fand punched.
